Date: 1997-10-08

Title: Static Colored SU(2) Sources in (1+1)-Dimensions - An Analytic Solution

in the Electric RepresentationAuthors: Jiannis Pachos and Antonios Tsapalis

Comments: 10 pages, 4 figs, REVTEX

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 1371-1382

Within the Schroedinger Electric Representation we analytically calculate thecomplete wave functional obeying Gauss' law with static SU(2) sources in(1+1)-dimensions. The effective potential is found to be linear in the distancebetween the sources as expected.